40
00:01:31.320 --> 00:01:33.560
So we're gonna read both.

41
00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:35.960
John chapter eight and verse 12.

42
00:01:35.960 --> 00:01:38.400
Again, Jesus spoke to them saying,

43
00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:40.680
I am the light of the world.

44
00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:44.760
