46
00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:49.280
John chapter nine.

47
00:01:50.440 --> 00:01:54.560
As he passed by, he saw a man blind from birth.

48
00:01:54.600 --> 00:01:56.720
And his disciples asked him, Rabbi,

49
00:01:56.720 --> 00:01:58.000
