114
00:04:42.540 --> 00:04:44.380
give glory to God.

115
00:04:44.380 --> 00:04:46.620
We know that this man is a sinner.

116
00:04:46.620 --> 00:04:49.300
He answered, whether he is a sinner or not,

117
00:04:49.300 --> 00:04:54.300
one thing I do, whether he is a sinner, I do not know.

118
00:04:54.700 --> 00:04:59.460
One thing I do know, that though I was blind, now I see.

119
00:04:59.460 --> 00:05:02.300
They said to him, what did he do to you?

120
00:05:02.300 --> 00:05:04.100
How did he open your eyes?

121
00:05:04.100 --> 00:05:06.300
He answered, I have told you already

122
00:05:06.300 --> 00:05:08.060
and you would not listen.

123
00:05:08.060 --> 00:05:09.380
Why do you want to hear it again?

124
00:05:09.380 --> 00:05:12.300
Do you also want to become his disciples?

125
00:05:12.300 --> 00:05:15.700
They reviled him saying, you are his disciple,

126
00:05:15.700 --> 00:05:18.900
but we are disciples of Moses.

127
00:05:18.900 --> 00:05:20.940
We know that God has spoken to Moses,

128
00:05:20.940 --> 00:05:25.940
but as for this man, we do not know where he comes from.

129
00:05:25.940 --> 00:05:29.100
The man answered, why this is an amazing thing.

130
00:05:29.100 --> 00:05:30.660
You do not know where he comes from

131
00:05:30.660 --> 00:05:33.180
and yet he opened my eyes.

132
00:05:33.180 --> 00:05:35.260
We know that God does not listen to sinners,

133
00:05:35.260 --> 00:05:38.260
but if anyone is a worshipper of God and does his will,

134
00:05:38.260 --> 00:05:40.220
God listens to him.

135
00:05:40.220 --> 00:05:42.620
Never since the world began has it been heard

136
00:05:42.620 --> 00:05:46.340
