140
00:05:56.740 --> 00:05:58.020
And they cast him out.

141
00:05:59.480 --> 00:06:02.660
Jesus heard that they had cast him out

142
00:06:02.660 --> 00:06:05.100
and having found him, he said,

143
00:06:05.100 --> 00:06:07.540
