144
00:06:07.540 --> 00:06:09.980
He answered, who is he, sir?

145
00:06:10.020 --> 00:06:12.100
That I may believe in him.

146
00:06:12.100 --> 00:06:15.300
Jesus said to him, you have seen him

147
00:06:15.300 --> 00:06:18.180
and it is he who is speaking to you.

148
00:06:18.180 --> 00:06:22.380
He said, Lord, I believe and he worshiped him.

149
00:06:22.380 --> 00:06:26.020
Jesus said, for judgment I came into this world

150
00:06:26.020 --> 00:06:29.060
that those who do not see may see

151
00:06:30.020 --> 00:06:34.220
and those who see may become blind.

152
00:06:34.220 --> 00:06:36.580
Some of the Pharisees near him heard these things

153
00:06:36.620 --> 00:06:40.140
and said to him, are we also blind?

154
00:06:40.140 --> 00:06:43.180
And Jesus said to them, if you were blind,

155
00:06:43.180 --> 00:06:44.820
you would have no guilt.

156
00:06:44.820 --> 00:06:49.540
But now that you say, we see your guilt remains.

157
00:06:49.540 --> 00:06:51.020
This is the word of the Lord.

158
00:06:52.620 --> 00:06:53.460
Let's pray.

159
00:06:59.220 --> 00:07:00.500
Lord, you are the God who said,

160
00:07:00.500 --> 00:07:03.700
let light shine out of darkness.

161
00:07:04.500 --> 00:07:06.420
Lord, I pray that by your light

162
00:07:06.420 --> 00:07:08.060
you would shine into our hearts

163
00:07:08.060 --> 00:07:10.620
that we may see the light of the knowledge

164
00:07:10.620 --> 00:07:13.820
of the glory of God in the face of Jesus.

165
00:07:14.700 --> 00:07:17.060
Lord, I pray that you would help us to trust

166
00:07:17.060 --> 00:07:18.660
and to follow him.

167
00:07:18.660 --> 00:07:20.700
What's in his name we pray, amen.

168
00:07:22.500 --> 00:07:25.460
When I was a kid, I wasn't a big fan of school

169
00:07:25.460 --> 00:07:26.900
but I was a big fan of field trips

170
00:07:26.900 --> 00:07:29.460
and one of my favorite field trips to go on

171
00:07:29.460 --> 00:07:31.540
was to DeSoto Caverns State Park.

172
00:07:31.540 --> 00:07:33.220
I don't know if any of you have been there before.

173
00:07:33.220 --> 00:07:35.420
You go to the big cave and I remember enjoying

174
00:07:35.420 --> 00:07:37.420
all the things that you could see in the cave

175
00:07:37.420 --> 00:07:39.980
but I also enjoyed a part of the tour

176
00:07:39.980 --> 00:07:42.620
where they would actually turn all the lights off

177
00:07:42.620 --> 00:07:45.100
in the cave, because you've not experienced darkness

178
00:07:45.100 --> 00:07:47.780
