199
00:08:35.340 --> 00:08:37.140
before they were rescued.

200
00:08:37.140 --> 00:08:40.340
So light was absolutely essential and they didn't have it.

201
00:08:40.340 --> 00:08:42.180
Can you imagine how frightening that would have been

202
00:08:42.180 --> 00:08:44.500
or the kind of hope that you'd be hit with,

203
00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:46.060
the joy that would come over you

204
00:08:46.060 --> 00:08:49.780
