00:10:07.180 --> 00:10:09.600
But also light is essential not just for sight,

236
00:10:09.600 --> 00:10:11.300
but for life.

237
00:10:11.300 --> 00:10:14.300
If you wanna do something frightening, Google,

238
00:10:14.300 --> 00:10:18.260
what would happen if the sun stopped shining?

239
00:10:18.260 --> 00:10:22.100
If the sun stopped shining in less than nine minutes,

240
00:10:22.100 --> 00:10:24.100
Earth would be in total darkness, right?

