00:10:54.660 --> 00:10:57.300
So those who have his light have life.

252
00:10:57.300 --> 00:10:58.900
It is the light of life.

253
00:10:58.900 --> 00:11:00.600
It's the difference between life and death,

254
00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:04.260
