255
00:11:04.260 --> 00:11:07.460
and to navigate our way through life.

256
00:11:07.460 --> 00:11:09.980
It is by his light that we truly see.

257
00:11:11.520 --> 00:11:13.300
But Jesus' statement here isn't just a kind of

