00:11:17.260 --> 00:11:20.660
It is, there's a particular context that he says this

261
00:11:20.660 --> 00:11:22.180
that helps us to understand this claim.

262
00:11:22.180 --> 00:11:24.260
Really, we're looking at chapter seven

263
00:11:24.260 --> 00:11:25.860
all the way through chapter nine here

264
00:11:25.860 --> 00:11:28.220
with what Jesus is claiming when he claims

265
00:11:28.220 --> 00:11:29.780
to be the light of the world.

266
00:11:29.780 --> 00:11:31.340
So what's the context?

267
00:11:31.340 --> 00:11:35.460
It's the feast of booths or the feast of tabernacles.

