287
00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:22.120
together in this kind of like camping festival.

288
00:12:22.120 --> 00:12:24.120
I don't know, you might think of like Woodstock

289
00:12:24.120 --> 00:12:28.800
or Burning Man or just without the drugs or all the other.

290
00:12:28.800 --> 00:12:30.000
It's don't think about that.

291
00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:31.280
Think about a family camping trip.

292
00:12:31.280 --> 00:12:33.840
It's like a family camping trip.

293
00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:38.120
The festival of tabernacles, the feast of booths.

294
00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:42.480
And like any camping trip, light was absolutely essential.

295
00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:44.480
It was an essential part of the wilderness wanderings

296
00:12:44.480 --> 00:12:45.320
for sure.

297
00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:47.080
When you look back at the wilderness wanderings,

298
00:12:47.080 --> 00:12:48.920
you see light all over the place.

299
00:12:48.920 --> 00:12:51.000
So as God is present among his people

300
00:12:51.000 --> 00:12:53.280
and guiding his people, he is present among them

301
00:12:53.280 --> 00:12:55.840
and guided them with a pillar of cloud by day

302
00:12:55.840 --> 00:12:58.640
