303
00:12:58.640 --> 00:13:02.680
So his light is guiding them through the wilderness.

304
00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:04.760
It was during that time that God gave them

305
00:13:04.760 --> 00:13:09.600
his law on Mount Sinai and where God is giving the law.

306
00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:11.840
There's this cloud that covers Mount Sinai

307
00:13:11.840 --> 00:13:15.160
and God makes himself known in fire that we're told

308
00:13:15.160 --> 00:13:18.640
as he is giving his law there on the mountains.

309
00:13:18.680 --> 00:13:20.200
You have light on the top of the mountain

310
00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:23.360
as God is giving guidance through his word.

311
00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:28.080
It's interesting to note that the Hebrew word for light

