00:13:36.680 --> 00:13:38.600
See a relationship between those two?

316
00:13:38.600 --> 00:13:40.400
So or Torah.

317
00:13:40.400 --> 00:13:42.440
So right in the middle of the Torah,

318
00:13:42.440 --> 00:13:44.480
these first five books of the Bible

319
00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:46.560
is this kind of play on words here.

320
00:13:46.560 --> 00:13:51.560
You have God is guiding us by the light of his word.

321
00:13:52.400 --> 00:13:55.400
So you then have like Psalm 119, 105,

322
00:13:55.400 --> 00:13:58.320
