324
00:14:01.120 --> 00:14:03.080
So the God who guided his people through the wilderness

325
00:14:03.080 --> 00:14:04.720
also guides his people by his word

326
00:14:04.720 --> 00:14:07.800
and all of that is described as light.

327
00:14:07.800 --> 00:14:09.440
Also during the Wondrings,

