00:15:43.960 --> 00:15:45.160
Do you see what he's saying?

369
00:15:45.160 --> 00:15:49.400
He's saying this God that you are celebrating, that's me.

370
00:15:49.400 --> 00:15:51.040
All of this is pointing to me.

371
00:15:51.040 --> 00:15:53.920
Yes, it's pointing back to him and what he did in the past

