00:17:17.740 --> 00:17:22.580
He says he's coming to be a light to the nations.

405
00:17:22.580 --> 00:17:27.580
That my salvation may reach to the ends of the earth.

406
00:17:27.980 --> 00:17:30.180
So God is a God of radiant glory

407
00:17:30.180 --> 00:17:31.900
and he saves his people

408
00:17:31.900 --> 00:17:35.020
but he is also going to save bring his salvation

409
00:17:35.020 --> 00:17:37.340
to the nations and the way he's going to bring

