00:17:54.180 --> 00:17:58.740
in him was life and the life was the light of man.

415
00:17:59.820 --> 00:18:04.140
He is the very glory of God tabernacle among us.

416
00:18:04.180 --> 00:18:06.220
John chapter one verse 14.

417
00:18:06.220 --> 00:18:07.660
So he's bringing salvation.

